latestIgtvVideos.title: Face mask for a glowing skin
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
To get a glowing , moisturised & nourished skin try this face mask 
Great for dry skin 
Please do a patch test on a small area before applying it to the full face , to check for allergies 
You will need:

Papaya peel
1 tbsp organic honey
2 Vitamin E capsules 
Massage while applying , leave it on for 10-15 mins (or until dry) & wash it off

latestIgtvVideos.title: Quick and easy summer makeup
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Less is more in this summer heat but makeup is bae! So here’s a super easy and minimal makeup look which will make you look 💯 without going OTT

Products used (after moisturiser and sunscreen) :
🔸Avene thermal spring water spray 🔸Huda beauty Rose Gold Palette (Sandalwood on the crease , Flamingo on the lid slightly mixed with Shy) 🔸Bobbi brown Long Wear Weightless Foundation ( I prefer a BB cream for the day but I was travelling and forgot to carry it 🙈) 🔸Nars Radiant Creamy Concealer 🔸Tarte Amazonian Clay Blush (soft nude peach) 🔸Laura Mercier Setting Powder 🔸Becca Liquid Highlighter (Champagne Pop) 🔸 Kylie Cosmetics Lipstick (Dirty Peach )
